                     <interp inst="t17690222-13-off70" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17690222-13-off70" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a silk gown, value 20 s. a linen gown, value 2 s. and a mahogany tea chest, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17690222-13-victim144" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
                     Tite 
                  <interp inst="t17690222-13-victim144" type="surname" value="Tite"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17690222-13-victim144" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
