               <p>The only evidence to the fact was 
               <persName id="t17690222-13-person158">
                  Ruben 
                  Biggs 
               <interp inst="t17690222-13-person158" type="surname" value="Biggs"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17690222-13-person158" type="given" value="Ruben"></interp>
