               <p>They were both <rs id="t17690222-13-verdict83" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17690222-13-verdict83" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               acquitted
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>There were three other indictments against them.</p>
               <p>See Smithson tried before, No. 16. and No. 342. in Mr. Alderman Nelson's mayoralty.</p>
